race.comment: FORGING AHEAD (2) has hit the top-five in all five career outings to date and looks to be on the doorstep of a maiden victory. Ready for the step-up to the mile journey now and should be right there when the whips are cracking. FRANKELY SUBLIME (7) was too bad to be true last time out but the form prior was good enough for a race of this calibre. Capable of bouncing right back. CARAMELFUDGESUNDAE (9) has finished runner-up in two of her past three and will be at peak fitness for this. In the mix. BANXI (1) is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley and gets the reliable Waller/Maloney combination. Don't dismiss lightly. ARTISTIC TOUCH (5) rounds out the selections at odds.
